---
import KlikboxSeoAiLayout from "../../layouts/KlikboxSeoAiLayout.astro";
---
<KlikboxSeoAiLayout
  title="Terms of Service - Klikbox SEO AI"
  description="Terms of service for Klikbox SEO AI, a Shopify app by Klikbox."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <article class="legal-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: May 24, 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Agreement</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms of Service apply to merchants who install or use Klikbox SEO AI,
        a Shopify app operated by Klikbox. By installing or using the app, you agree
        to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2>2. What the app does</h2>
      <p>
        Klikbox SEO AI helps merchants audit product SEO fields, generate AI draft
        copy, review suggested changes, and apply approved updates to product SEO
        titles, meta descriptions, and product descriptions.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Merchant responsibility</h2>
      <p>
        AI-generated drafts should be reviewed before publishing. Merchants are
        responsible for checking that product copy is accurate, lawful, and appropriate
        for their products, customers, and market.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Shopify account and permissions</h2>
      <p>
        The app requires Shopify permissions that support product catalog auditing and
        product updates. If permissions are removed, some app features may stop working.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Billing</h2>
      <p>
        Paid plans, if selected, are billed through Shopify Billing. Shopify handles
        payment approval, billing, and subscription management. Plan limits and pricing
        are shown in the Shopify App Store listing and inside the app.
      </p>

      <h2>6. AI draft limits</h2>
      <p>
        Monthly draft limits depend on the selected plan. Unused drafts may not roll
        over to future months unless explicitly stated in the app.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Support</h2>
      <p>
        Support is available by email at
        <a href="mailto:klikboxofficial@gmail.com">klikboxofficial@gmail.com</a>.
        We aim to respond to support requests within a reasonable time.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Availability</h2>
      <p>
        We work to keep the app available and functional, but we do not guarantee
        uninterrupted access. Service interruptions may occur due to maintenance,
        hosting issues, third-party API issues, or Shopify platform changes.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>Merchants must not use the app to create or publish content that is illegal, deceptive, or violates Shopify policies.</p>

      <h2>10. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Klikbox is not liable for indirect,
        incidental, or consequential damages related to use of the app. The app provides
        draft content and workflow tools, not legal, financial, or professional advice.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms as the app changes. Continued use of the app after
        changes are posted means you accept the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2>12. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Email: <a href="mailto:klikboxofficial@gmail.com">klikboxofficial@gmail.com</a><br />
        Website: <a href="https://klikbox.gr">https://klikbox.gr</a>
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="aside">
      <h3>Plain-language note</h3>
      <p>Review AI drafts before applying them. The merchant stays in control of product updates.</p>
      <p class="meta">Billing is handled through Shopify Billing.</p>
    </aside>
  </section>
</KlikboxSeoAiLayout>
